Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:19:00.51,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}車寬：2.14m
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:19:00.51,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}主炮：37mm炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:19:00.51,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}追獵者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:19:00.51,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}重量：15.75t
